00:48:21.130 --> 00:48:24.220
In "The Martian," it was really
just all about spreadsheets.

00:48:24.220 --> 00:48:26.770
And I wrote some
software of my own

00:48:26.770 --> 00:48:29.657
for calculating the orbital
trajectories that people took.

00:48:29.657 --> 00:48:31.030
AUDIENCE: That's awesome.

