00:49:22.337 --> 00:49:23.680
for it, but I mean--

00:49:23.680 --> 00:49:25.300
AUDIENCE: So my
question is just,

00:49:25.300 --> 00:49:28.200
how much time did
you spend developing

00:49:28.200 --> 00:49:30.430
the science and the
