Now, the science I blew through
in like a few weeks of just--

00:49:46.780 --> 00:49:48.400
that stuff is so fun to me.

00:49:48.400 --> 00:49:52.620
I just-- I'll just stay up
late working on that crap.

00:49:52.620 --> 00:49:55.750
But the characters and stuff,
that was time-consuming.

00:49:55.750 --> 00:49:58.900
Also at the same time, I was
working on a different book.

00:49:58.900 --> 00:50:00.880
Between "The "Martian
and "Artemis,"

00:50:00.880 --> 00:50:02.920
